90_text","default":"<p>2</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggrjkLuav32_text","label":"ggrjkLuav32_text","default":"Then we reduce harmful bacteria"},{"type":"html","id":"gg4kmeLNBq__text","label":"gg4kmeLNBq__text","default":"<p>An imbalanced gut often means harmful bacteria have started to dominate. Instead of harsh elimination, GemGut uses natural prebiotic fibers to gently shift the ecosystem.</p><p>These fibers act as nourishment for beneficial bacteria while making it harder for harmful microbes to thrive. Over time, this helps rebalance your gut in a sustainable, non-aggressive way—without disrupting your body’s natural rhythm.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggAtHTrsFA4_text","label":"ggAtHTrsFA4_text","default":"<p>3</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggfTpx5ZIgt_text","label":"ggfTpx5ZIgt_text","default":"We reintroduce beneficial bacteria"},{"type":"html","id":"ggTlLhKKhqu_text","label":"ggTlLhKKhqu_text","default":"<p>With the gut environment improved, live probiotic cultures (Lactobacillus &amp; Bifidobacterium) are able to settle and begin restoring a healthy microbiome.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggPf9_rEacR_text","label":"ggPf9_rEacR_text","default":"<p>4</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg9h9cq3q1g_text","label":"gg9h9cq3q1g_text","default":"Your digestion starts working efficiently again"},{"type":"html","id":"ggqctov_oeF_text","label":"ggqctov_oeF_text","default":"<p>Plant-based enzymes and peppermint support faster breakdown of food, reducing bloating, heaviness, and post-meal discomfort—often within 30–60 minutes.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg9bWe5bOeM_text","label":"gg9bWe5bOeM_text","default":"<p>5</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggCxvUi54ZD_text","label":"ggCxvUi54ZD_text","default":"Your gut stays balanced and resilient"},{"type":"html","id":"gggWglH-5hF_text","label":"gggWglH-5hF_text","default":"<p>With consistent use, your gut becomes more stable, better at handling stress, and more efficient at absorbing nutrients—helping you feel lighter, more energized, and in control every day.</p>"}],
